  <body>
    <header><span>Select-No-of-Stockrooms</span></header>
    <h2>Basic Path</h2>
    <div class="basic-path">
      <ol>
	<li><p>The use case begins when the Inventory Manager selects
	    "Select-No-of-Stockrooms".</p></li>
	<li><p>The software retrieves the current number of stockrooms.</p></li>
	<li><p>The software prompts the Inventory Manager whether to use
	    one single stockroom or two stockrooms: one primary and one secondary.
	    The retrieves current number of stockrooms is used as a default.</p></li>
	<li><p>If the current number of stockrooms goes from one to two then
	    inventory within the first stockroom stays at the primary stockroom.</p></li>
	<li><p>If the current number of stockrooms goes from two to one then
	    the software prompts the Inventory manager whether to add the inventory
	    in the second stockroom to the first or to just remove the inventory.
	    The default is to add the inventory.</p></li>
	<li><p>The software adds the inventory from the second stockroom to the first
	    stockroom.</p></li>
	

    <h2>Alternate Paths</h2>
    <h3>DB Error</h3>
